title: (Tues Full) Eddie Pays Out His Punishment of Barking Like A Dog + 6th Grader Reese Gives an Update on Her Talent Show Performance
itunes:title: (Tues Full) Eddie Pays Out His Punishment of Barking Like A Dog + 6th Grader Reese Gives an Update on Her Talent Show Performance
description:
Eddie finally pays out his punishment of barking like a dog in a public place until someone asks him to stop. It doesn't go the way we thought it would. 6th Grader Reese lets us know how her performance of 1994 went at her talent show and how she feels after making the news!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
